<p>In this workshop the participants looked at a number of code listings grouped as pairs of alternative approaches to implement a certain test or tests. The following is a record of observations collected during the debriefing of this exercise.
</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc"><tr><td><div id="toctitle"><h2>Contents</h2></div>
<ul>
